summary:
- **Substantial holder change**: Capital DI Limited increased its holding in Asara Resources Ltd to 157.2 million ordinary shares (11.42% voting power) from 150 million shares (13.62%).  
- **Change details**:  
  - **25/07/25**: On-market purchase of 7.2 million shares for AUD 360,000.  
  - **05/08/25**: Dilution to 11.42% due to Asara issuing 275.3 million new shares.  

No other material information identified.
